article_title: New England Employee Benefits Council to host health, welfare compliance presentation

article_metadata.description: WALTHAM — The New England Employee Benefits Council will present “Are You Drowning in Health and Welfare Compliance Issues? Help is on the Way!” from 8:30 a.m. to noon April 14 at the  at the Waltham Woods Conference Center, 860 Winter St., Waltham.The half-day session is designed for employers and consultants looking to expand their understanding of the various laws that apply to welfare benefit arrangements and the ever-growing list of required disclosures for them.
